<h2 style="color: #1e293b; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">New Contact Us Query</h2>
<p style="color: #475569; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  You have received a new inquiry from the Vestra Vault landing page contact form. Here are the details:
</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 24px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 16px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
      <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Name</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 700;"><%= name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Email Address</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; color: #4f46e5; font-weight: 600;"><%= email %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding-bottom: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Message</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="font-size: 15px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= message %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  This query was sent automatically by the Vestra Vault platform.
</p>
